creator: AMarkets Ltd.
descriptionHtml:
AMarkets is a mobile trading application, which provides fast and easy access to financial markets and allows you to manage your trading accounts from your phone

✅ Main features:
- Access to 255 trading instruments: Forex, CFD, Metals, Cryptocurrency, Bonds, Commodities, Indices
- Access to MetaTrader 5 platform
- Free $10 000 Demo account
- Real-time quotes, convenient graphs and charts
- Latest news, market data and daily analytics from the Company
- Instant technical support
- Easy and convenient management of multiple accounts
- Access to the trading terminal
- High-level of security and account protection
- Simple verification system
- Quick and easy registration




🏆 Trade with Integrity, Professionalism and Transparency. Welcome to AMarkets
- Providing impeccable service since 2007
- Instant commission free deposit
- EUR, USD accounts
- Leverage up to 1:1000
- Spreads from 0.2, order execution from 0.03 sec
- 255 instruments for trading
- State-of-the-art trading platform MT5
+20% on first deposit



🏛 Your interests are protected:
- The Financial Commission, an independent regulator, protects traders' interests, providing insurance for up to €20 000 per claim
- AMarkets provides negative balance protection to each client
- AMarkets' execution quality complies with Verify My Trade’s execution standards
- In 2017 AMarkets performed its audit by Ernst&Young, a reputable global auditing firm. As confirmed by the audit results, the total cash balances in the Company’s accounts exceed the total liabilities to its clients.




More information about AMarkets:
https://www.amarkets.com/

creator: AMarkets Ltd.
descriptionHtml:
AMarkets app - quick access to the financial markets and your trading account straight from your mobile device

A perfect solution both for beginners and professional traders:

- efficient management of your trading accounts;
- 100% account security and negative balance protection;

Try your hand at trading with a free $10 000 demo account and get a deposit bonus on your live account.

Trade with a transparent and reliable broker.
Welcome to AMarkets!
